# near the current hole position. It first loads parameters from EMProperties and then
# determines an offset (delta_x, delta_y) derived from hole vectors (or from a previously
# saved Focus_position.txt). It then runs a selected hole-alignment routine to ensure the
# hole is centered, shifts to the carbon area by image shift, and repeatedly aligns the
